<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: py; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">def appen=
d_10(the_list=3D[]):
  the_list.append(10)
  return the_list</pre>=20
</div>
</div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"numberingColumn confluenceTd">3</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Use list comprehensions and generator express=
ions for concise and readable code.</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><u>Good</u></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">=20
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: py; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">fruits =
=3D ["apple", "banana", "cherry", "kiwi", "mango"]

newlist =3D [x for x in fruits if "a" in x]

print(newlist)</pre>=20
</div>
</div><p><u>Bad</u></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
